title: Grateful Dead Live at Giants Stadium on 1992-06-14
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-2 > Tascam CDRW2000 > CDR > EAC >  Wavelab > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 Tagged.
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Walkin' Blues, Candyman, Desolation Row, Jack A Roe, Picasso Moon, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Way To Go Home, Corinna, Drums-> Jam*-> Spoonful*, The Other One*, Morning Dew*, E:Baba O'Riley-> E: Tomorrow Never Knows

* with Steve Miller, guitar.  Steve Miller Band Opened.
